item.title: US-26 East - Fort Laramie
item.description: Entering Fort Laramie on US-26 west. Elevation 4320. Population 230. The town of Fort Laramie is adjacent to the site of the old Fort Laramie at the confluence of the Laramie River and the North Platte River.
